data.value: -v0.4 Beta(pre release): +Player movements and the hitbox have been improved +The game can support more than 100 enemies +Three new enemies +Rework NPC-uri / AI +New settings +Reflections on some objects and SSR +Better LOD +Better post processing and lighting +new models +New details for map (level design) +Optimization +Grass rework +Dynamic weather +Dynamic clouds +Night-day cycle +Rain +New fog +New skybox +New sounds +Photo mode +Barricade improvements +Two cars were added +New items ---------------------------------- -v0.3 Beta: +Perks have been improved +Weapon upgrades have been changed +The console has new commands and received a small rework +The UI has been improved +Enemies have new models (new design) +EasterEggs +New enemies +Dirt lens for bloom effect +The difficulty of the game received small changes +Advance settings for levels +Tutorial +Clouds are generated randomly +Weapon changes: PSL (Buff), ASALT96 (Nerf) +Weapons informations are better +The HE grenade was added +Weapons skins +New settings +New footstep sounds +New decals for bullets +Player skills system +Player profiles were added: ranks, levels, stats, player profile +The game has promo codes +Achievements +New animations +New sounds +The lighting has been modified +Post Processing has been modified +The map has been enlarged (100m x 100m -> 1km x 1km) ---------------------------------- -v0.2 Beta: Pause In-game Settings Un nou efect de Sway weapon Un nou movement pentru jucator O noua tinta Music system New menu Preloader Select level and difficulty menu Wave System Loading screen Inamicii sa aiba o bara de viata Adauga sunete pt butoane (3) Bonus System New terrain Volumetric cloud New enemies Chest bonus Perks Bullet proof vest Noi detalii Inventory Items Crafting Building Stats, Weapons upgrades si Consola cu comenzi ---------------------------------- -v0.1 Beta: +Enemies; +Movement; +Weapons;

data.name: AboutLabel.Text
data.value: The Bean is an indie First-Person Shooter game/FPS game(lowpoly and offline/singleplayer), created by one person with UnityEngine.ln this game you are a bean that you have to survive as many waves as possible ... it's simple
